Determing the band gap using hybrid (HSE06) energy functional

For a reasonably quick test

ecut 400
ngkpt 9 9 9
fockdownsampling 3*3
--> overestimates E_g ~ 1.4 eV


Better accuracy

ecut 500
ngkpt 10 10 10
fockdownsampling 3*2
--> reaches E_g ~ 1.2 eV

... convergence of ecut, ngkpt, and mesh for Fock operator calculation must be converged...


Benchmark paper: https://doi.org/10.1021/acs.jctc.9b00322

HSE06 paper: https://doi.org/10.1063/1.2404663


Abinit documentation page for running hybrid calculations:
https://docs.abinit.org/topics/Hybrids/
